Although in different places, &quot;anarchism&quot; is variously understood as being either socialist or capitalist, when unadorned, however, anarchism popularly denotes libertarian socialism, communism, socialism, democracy,pacifism, and syndicalism, libertarian communists, left-anarchists, anarcho-communists, anarcosocial-communists, and green anarchists
