---------------[12]
Although in some circles anarchism is perceived to be a terrorist philosophy, anarchists dispute this and consider themselves to be part of a movement which contains, libertarian socialism, communism, socialism, democracy, pacifism, syndicalism, libertarian communism, left-anarchism, anarcho-communism, anarchosocial-communism, green anarchism, anarcho-primitivism, anarcho-feminism, individualist anarchism, andor red anarchism
Other variations include syndicalism, libertarian communism, left-anarchism, anarcho-communism, anarchosocial-communism, green anarchism, anarcho-primitivism, anarcho-feminism, individualist anarchism, red anarchism, and anarcho-capitalism
