---------------[12]
Collectivist and individualist anarchists tend to deny that anarcho-capitalism is a form of anarchism, often based upon the argument that anarchism entails opposition to elements of capitalism they consider coercive
Traditional anarchists tend to deny that anarcho-capitalism is a form of anarchism, often based upon the argument that anarchism entails opposition to elements of capitalism they consider coercive
