---------------[39]
In realistic cases, a Bidirectional reflectance distribution function (BRDF) is required to accurately characterise the scattering properties of a surface, although albedos are a very useful first approcimation
In realistic cases, a Bidirectional reflectance distribution function (BRDF) is required to accurately characterise the scattering properties of a surface, although albedos are a very useful first approximation
