---------------[307]
His leadership qualities were evident in his first diplomatic handling of the border slave states at the beginning of the fighting, in his defeat of a congressional attempt to reorganize his cabinet in 1862, in his many speeches and writings which helped mobilize and inspire the North, and in his defusing of the peace issue in the 1864 presidential campaign
His leadership qualities were evident in his diplomatic handling of the border slave states at the beginning of the fighting, his defeat of a Congressional attempt to reorganize his cabinet in 1862, and in his defusion of the peace issue in the 1864 presidential campaign
